---
// Categories — griglia asimmetrica mix occasioni + prodotti (decorative, no link)
---
<section class="bg-cream pb-24 md:pb-32">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6" data-reveal>
      <span class="w-8 h-px bg-ink"></span>
      <span class="eyebrow text-ink/70">— cosa stampiamo</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-end justify-between flex-wrap gap-6 mb-14">
      <h2 class="font-display-tight text-6xl md:text-8xl text-ink leading-[0.9]" data-reveal>
        Tutto.<br><span class="text-orange">Davvero tutto.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-ink/70 text-lg max-w-md" data-reveal>
        Sei occasioni, tante categorie prodotto, migliaia di articoli. Sotto trovate la versione corta.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 grid-rows-3 md:grid-rows-2 gap-4 md:gap-5 auto-rows-[180px] md:auto-rows-[260px]">
      <!-- 01 · KIT DI BENVENUTO — hero card (col-span-2 row-span-2) -->
      <div
        class="cat-card relative col-span-2 row-span-2 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between"
        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FE5000 0%, #FFB371 100%);"
        data-reveal
      >
        <span class="eyebrow text-cream/80">01 · kit di benvenuto aziendali</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display-tight text-cream text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[0.9]">Il primo giorno,<br>il primo regalo.</h3>
          <p class="cat-tag text-cream/90 mt-4 text-sm font-bold">borraccia + taccuino + t-shirt + shopper, dal vostro brand</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 02 · DRINKWARE -->
      <div
        class="cat-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden p-5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-navy text-cream"
        data-reveal
      >
        <span class="eyebrow text-cream/60">02 · drinkware</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl leading-tight break-words hyphens-auto" lang="it">Tazze, borracce, thermos.</h3>
          <p class="cat-tag text-cream/70 mt-2 text-xs font-bold">→ 4.100+ articoli</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 03 · TECH -->
      <div
        class="cat-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden p-5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-cream text-ink border-2 border-ink/10"
        data-reveal
      >
        <span class="eyebrow text-ink/70">03 · tech</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl leading-tight break-words hyphens-auto" lang="it">USB, batteria portatile, cuffie.</h3>
          <p class="cat-tag text-ink/70 mt-2 text-xs font-bold">→ 3.800+ articoli</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 04 · EVENTI & FIERE -->
      <div
        class="cat-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden p-5 flex flex-col justify-between text-cream"
        style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1C1F2A 0%, #292929 100%);"
        data-reveal
      >
        <span class="eyebrow text-orange">04 · gadget per eventi e fiere</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl leading-tight break-words hyphens-auto" lang="it">Stand, omaggi, staff.</h3>
          <p class="cat-tag text-cream/70 mt-2 text-xs font-bold">cordini, t-shirt staff, shopper, batterie portatili per il vostro evento</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 05 · ECO-CORPORATE -->
      <div
        class="cat-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden p-5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-orange-pale text-ink"
        data-reveal
      >
        <span class="eyebrow text-ink/70">05 · gadget ecosostenibili</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl leading-tight break-words hyphens-auto" lang="it">RPET, bambù, cotone bio.</h3>
          <p class="cat-tag text-ink/70 mt-2 text-xs font-bold">→ 2.900+ articoli · certificati FSC/GOTS/OEKO-TEX</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- 06 · REGALI CORPORATE -->
      <div
        class="cat-card relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden p-5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-ink text-cream"
        data-reveal
      >
        <span class="eyebrow text-cream/60">06 · regali aziendali personalizzati</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display-tight text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl leading-tight break-words hyphens-auto" lang="it">Natale, milestone, anniversari.</h3>
          <p class="cat-tag text-cream/70 mt-2 text-xs font-bold">gift box, ceramica, accessori premium</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <p class="font-display-tight text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink leading-tight max-w-md">
        …e altre 24 categorie. <span class="text-ink/70">Sì, abbiamo contato.</span>
      </p>
      <a
        href="/catalogo"
        class="border-2 border-ink text-ink px-7 py-4 text-sm font-bold tracking-wide rounded-full hover:bg-ink hover:text-cream transition"
        style="text-decoration:none;"
      >
        Sfoglia il catalogo (484 pagine) →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
